00:14:49.082 --> 00:14:56.447
rather than Esau, the firstborn of Yitschaq,

00:14:56.527 --> 00:14:57.967
who was passed over.

00:14:59.203 --> 00:15:01.706
Our status and standing with God are

00:15:01.765 --> 00:15:06.230
therefore based upon character and not

00:15:06.289 --> 00:15:10.332
always on chronology.

00:15:10.373 --> 00:15:11.533
Shamuwʿel by contrast,

00:15:11.594 --> 00:15:13.995
was the firstborn child of Hannah.

00:15:14.696 --> 00:15:17.339
His birth required divine intervention,

00:15:17.859 --> 00:15:20.441
making his story different than the

00:15:20.500 --> 00:15:22.282
others, with the exception, of course,

00:15:22.322 --> 00:15:22.962
of Yitschaq.

00:15:23.783 --> 00:15:27.125
It reveals that Yahowah's approach to those

00:15:27.166 --> 00:15:27.307
who

00:15:28.381 --> 00:15:29.722
not only search for him,

00:15:29.842 --> 00:15:32.745
but who come to know and rely upon

00:15:32.884 --> 00:15:35.527
him, matters to him.

00:15:36.008 --> 00:15:39.409
Hannah's speech during Shamuw’el's

00:15:39.629 --> 00:15:40.451
dedication,

00:15:40.471 --> 00:15:42.932
that would be first Samuel two,

00:15:43.373 --> 00:15:44.114
one through ten,

00:15:44.673 --> 00:15:46.535
is so insightful and inspiring,

00:15:46.655 --> 00:15:47.416
in due course,

00:15:48.057 --> 00:15:49.557
we'll ponder its implications.

00:15:49.977 --> 00:15:50.518
But for now,

00:15:50.899 --> 00:15:53.721
suffice it to say that the resulting son

00:15:53.821 --> 00:15:57.504
was resolute when it

00:15:58.297 --> 00:16:01.437
came to acting on Yahowah's instructions.

00:16:02.198 --> 00:16:04.740
So Yahowah's Bakowr, firstborn son,

00:16:05.720 --> 00:16:08.140
is the eighth born of Yshay

00:16:08.902 --> 00:16:11.923
So to be God's firstborn when he's the

00:16:12.023 --> 00:16:13.803
eighth born to Yshay

00:16:14.283 --> 00:16:16.384
there was another qualification to cause

00:16:16.465 --> 00:16:19.365
Dowd to be called Yahowah's Bakowr,

00:16:19.405 --> 00:16:19.986
firstborn.

00:16:20.626 --> 00:16:24.928
And if I were to surmise a conclusion

00:16:24.948 --> 00:16:25.349
to that,

00:16:25.948 --> 00:16:27.769
I think it's obvious that

00:16:28.493 --> 00:16:31.414
The only way that Dowd has the title

00:16:31.455 --> 00:16:32.895
bakowr, firstborn of God,

00:16:33.456 --> 00:16:37.019
is he's the first human with a conscience,

00:16:37.038 --> 00:16:37.620
an neshamah,

00:16:38.460 --> 00:16:41.923
