So he sent away for him and brought

00:17:01.801 --> 00:17:02.001
him.

00:17:02.621 --> 00:17:07.624
He was ruddy and red headed.

00:17:08.403 --> 00:17:11.365
He was wa huwʾ ʾadmowny

00:17:11.944 --> 00:17:13.786
