00:17:41.520 --> 00:17:46.464
that this person would be my so-and-so.

00:17:46.505 --> 00:17:47.204
In this case,

00:17:48.005 --> 00:17:51.907
all things pertaining to my Adam.

00:17:54.368 --> 00:17:56.230
So he sent for him and he brought

00:17:56.250 --> 00:17:59.273
him and he was Adam.

00:18:01.756 --> 00:18:06.240
I like it when God shows such clever

00:18:06.280 --> 00:18:09.683
