Now, you could say,

00:18:54.415 --> 00:18:55.856
as I did when I first wrote this,

00:18:55.916 --> 00:18:58.198
because I had no clue of this three

00:18:58.238 --> 00:18:58.719
years ago.

00:18:59.019 --> 00:18:59.719
Three years ago,

00:19:00.179 --> 00:19:03.661
