That's what it says here.

00:20:38.471 --> 00:20:40.872
He was ʾadmowny

00:20:41.372 --> 00:20:41.853
He was Adam.

00:20:44.733 --> 00:20:49.576
I'm convinced that, well,

00:20:49.616 --> 00:20:52.278
the soul that resided within Adam,

00:20:53.239 --> 00:20:55.381
