00:21:21.569 --> 00:21:27.031
Dowd during the Exodus to keep

00:21:28.132 --> 00:21:30.473
Moshe going, Moshe upright,

00:21:30.733 --> 00:21:32.934
giving Moshe a sense that I know things.

