was attractive and beautiful, cheerful.

00:22:45.903 --> 00:22:47.523
Um, and can be, you know, eyes,

00:22:48.003 --> 00:22:50.385
perspective, uh, view of life.

00:22:50.705 --> 00:22:53.926
Um, any of those things would, uh,

00:22:53.967 --> 00:22:55.087
prevail in this case.

00:22:55.548 --> 00:22:59.029
And it says he was, uh, visually pleasing,

00:22:59.609 --> 00:23:03.152
uh, raʿy towb

00:23:03.211 --> 00:23:04.553
His appearance was beautiful,

00:23:04.613 --> 00:23:06.614
proportioned and desirable.

00:23:07.374 --> 00:23:09.535
And seeing him was exceptionally pleasant,

