Because indeed, this is he.

00:26:22.433 --> 00:26:24.775
First Samuel, 16:11 and 12

00:26:24.875 --> 00:26:29.537
So, Dowd was undeniably God's choice.

00:26:30.777 --> 00:26:31.917
Not the mythical Jesus.

00:26:33.417 --> 00:26:37.219
Not Shimon Bar Kokhba.

00:26:38.099 --> 00:26:38.740
Not Muhammad.

00:26:40.709 --> 00:26:45.436
And at this point, God knew him well.

